	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div xml:id="div1" corresp="regest1">
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Accepisti nostra<note xml:id="fn1" type="footnote" n="1">Gemeint ist sicher <persName ref="p8055" cert="high">Blarers</persName> Brief vom 6. August, oben <ref target="file11691">Nr. 1648</ref>.</note>, puto, mi venerande <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495" cert="high">Bullingere</persName>, quę per illum ipsum bonum virum<note xml:id="fn2" type="footnote" n="2">Unbekannt.</note>, qui tuas nobis literas<note xml:id="fn3" type="footnote" n="3">Ein Brief <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495" cert="high">Bullingers</persName> aus dieser Zeit ist nicht erhalten.</note> reddidit, misimus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Praeterea nihil est, quod addamus extra illa, quę <persName ref="p2810" cert="low" type="citizen_name">Erasmus</persName> noster<note xml:id="fn4" type="footnote" n="4"><persName ref="p8437" cert="high">Erasmus Schmid</persName> oder <persName ref="p2810" cert="high">Erasmus Ritter</persName>.</note> narrare tibi potuit, in quem pariter et optimos viros, quibus facundum se comitem adiunxit, utinam tam humanis et officiosis esse nobis<note xml:id="fna" type="footnote" n="a">nobis <hi>über der Zeile nachgetragen.</hi></note> licuisset, quam sunt illi modis omnibus dignissimi.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Sed omnis fere negata nobis occasio fuit, tum quod retineri se diutius non sunt passi, tum quod <persName ref="p4079" cert="high">Zviccius</persName> noster<note xml:id="fn5" type="footnote" n="5"><persName ref="p4079" cert="high">Johannes Zwick</persName>.</note> adesse illis non potuit; quum enim ad quosdam peste correptos vocaretur, noluit deinde cum illis congredi, ne quid forte mali (ut serpit hic morbus contagio) affricaret<note xml:id="fn6" type="footnote" n="6">Zum Ausbruch der Pest im Spätsommer 1542 und <persName ref="p4079" cert="high">Zwicks</persName> Engagement für die Pestkranken v. a. in der Gemeinde <placeName ref="l50" cert="high">Bischofszell</placeName> vgl. <hi>Moeller,</hi> <persName ref="p4079" cert="high">Zwick</persName> 233, 243.</note>.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Videtur nos omnino dominus hoc etiam anno quemadmodum superiore castigaturus,<note xml:id="fn7" type="footnote" n="7">1541 bis 1543 wurde <placeName ref="l457" cert="high">Konstanz</placeName> von drei Pestwellen, die jeweils im Sommer einsetzten, heimgesucht; vgl. <hi>Moeller,</hi> <persName ref="p4079" cert="high">Zwick</persName> 233.</note> quare illi nos cum tuis christianę[!] commendabis, ut vel vivamus ad ipsius gloriam vel fluxam et evanidam hanc vitam cum ęterna commutemus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="18770" type="citizen_name" cert="high">Brunsvicensis</persName><note xml:id="fn8" type="footnote" n="8"><persName ref="p18770" cert="high">Herzog Heinrich d.J. von Braunschweig-Wolfenbüttel</persName>.</note> fuga sibi consuluit et ad <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l619" cert="high">Baioarię</placeName> opidulum <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l276" cert="high">Landtsperg</placeName> cum paucissimis se contulit<note xml:id="fn9" type="footnote" n="9"><persName type="citizen_name" ref="p18770" cert="high">Heinrich</persName> flüchtete mit seinen Söhnen <persName ref="p18720" cert="high">Karl Viktor</persName> und <persName cert="high" type="citizen_name" ref="p20267">Philipp Magnus</persName> sowie seinem Kanzler <persName ref="p20004" cert="high">Stopler</persName> nach <placeName ref="l276" cert="high">Landshut</placeName>; vgl. <bibl>Otto</bibl> von <hi>Heinemann,</hi> Geschichte von <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l1041" cert="high">Braunschweig</placeName> und <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l205" cert="high">Hannover</placeName>, Bd. 2, Gotha 1886, S. 360f; <hi>Blume,</hi> Goslar 108; vgl. auch unten <ref target="file11695">Nr. 1652</ref>, 1-7; 1673 (Beilage); 1700, 57f.</note>.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quid porro futurum sit, expectamus.<pb type="edition" next="162"/></s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Salutant te nostri omnes.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Salutabis totam tuam domum cum omnibus fratribus et amicis.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Bene vale, suavissime pectus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l457" cert="high">Constantiae</placeName>, 9. augusti 1542.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tuus <persName ref="p8055" cert="high">Ambr. Blaurerus</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="address">[Adresse auf der Rückseite:]</note>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495" cert="high">Bullingero</persName> suo.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
